            "description": "<p>The fanged skull rune begins speaking in sweet, honeyed tones about eternal life.</p>",
            "disable": "<p><span data-pf2-check=\"religion\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Exorcise Spirit DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Religion</span> (trained) to exorcise the spirit, <span data-pf2-check=\"religion\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Sever Spiritual Connection DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Religion</span> or <span data-pf2-check=\"occultism\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Sever Spiritual Connection DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Occultism</span> (trained) to sever the connection between <em>Hunger's Call</em> and the temple, or <span data-pf2-check=\"athletics\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Crack the Wall DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Athletics</span> to crack the wall in several places; three total successes are required to disable the haunt.</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
                "value": 3
            },
            "reset": "<p>The mosaic ceases its routine 2 rounds after all living creatures are out of sight of the stairs. After 6 hours the haunt is ready to trigger again.</p>",
